1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:11,020
Sometimes I can’t believe we have come this far, Kuku!

2
00:00:11,180 --> 00:00:19,040
Just LOOK at this old photo! I used to be so skinny!

3
00:00:20,140 --> 00:00:26,200
I was skinny alright...and poor! Just look at the homes we used to live in!

4
00:00:27,130 --> 00:00:32,170
We definitely have come a long way, Kuku.

5
00:00:32,240 --> 00:00:42,000
And what an adventure it has been! Remember when we dug the first oil well?

6
00:00:42,210 --> 00:00:48,300
I felt like an explorer out there in the desert. Not a soul to be seen for MILES!

7
00:00:50,150 --> 00:00:55,150
What great memories, Kuku.

8
00:00:55,270 --> 00:01:02,200
Makes me very proud of what we have accomplished.

9
00:01:03,140 --> 00:01:09,000
Like they say, Kuku, good things come to those who wait...

10
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:18,000
...and to those who take a chance, too!
